OL,3,CMan charged with north Belfast murder
OL,5,FA 41-year-old man has been charged
OL,6,Fwith murder following the death of a
OL,7,Fman in north Belfast.
OL,9,F44-year-old Paul Mackin Jr, was
OL,10,Freportedly assaulted at a residential
OL,11,Fproperty in the Duncairn Parade area
OL,12,Fon Monday.
OL,14,FThe man has been charged with murder,
OL,15,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent, and
OL,16,Ffalse imprisonment as part of the
OL,17,Fongoing investigation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/2
