OL,3,CMan charged with north Belfast murder
OL,5,FPolice also confirmed that a report
OL,6,Fwill be submitted to the Public
OL,7,FProsecution Service (PPS) relating to
OL,8,Fa number of additional alleged
OL,9,Foffences.
OL,11,FThe accused is scheduled to appear
OL,12,Fbefore Belfast Magistrates' Court on
OL,13,FFriday.
OL,15,FThe PSNI noted that, as is standard
OL,16,Fprocedure, all charges will be
OL,17,Freviewed by the Public Prosecution
OL,18,FService.
OL,20,FThe investigation into the murder of
OL,21,FPaul Mackin Junior remains ongoing.
